Node:	shake_head (Motion response representing "no")
Input:
	String speech
Config:
	keyword ["hate","no","shut up"]
Output:
	bool success
Steps:
	Initialization: begin subscribing to tpc_speech (10Hz)
	1. 	if keyword is detected, then
			(a) Make a request to srv_head_movement (40)
			(b) Make a request to srv_head_movement (140)
			(c) Make a request to srv_head_movement (40)
			(d) Make a request to srv_head_movement (140)
			(e) Make a request to srv_head_movement (90)
			(f) Return true
